code: export var useDrivesFilter=function useDrivesFilter(drivesList,filterValue){function filtered(drivesList,filterValue){switch(filterValue){case"available":return drivesList.filter(function(drive){return drive.rentalProjects.length===0;});case"unavailable":return drivesList.filter(function(drive){return drive.rentalProjects.length===1;});case"all":return drivesList;}}var filteredList=filtered(drivesList,filterValue);return filteredList;};
